#BNF+IAT 1.0 UTF-8;
!grammar call;
!slot <hold>;
!slot <light>;
!slot <window>;
!slot <open>;
!slot <close>;
!start <commands>;  //定义主规则
<commands>:<controlLight>|<controlWindow>;
<controlLight>:<open><light>|[<hold>]<light><open>|<close><light>|[<hold>]<light><close>;
<controlWindow>:<open><window>|[<hold>]<window><open>|<close><window>|[<hold>]<window><close>;
<hold>:把;
<open>:开|开一下|打开;
<close>:关|关一下|关闭|关掉;
<light>:灯|灯光|日光灯;
<window>:窗|窗户;
